original:
Yo! Thanks for comin'!
The name's Octomon!
Got any 'Spare Plates'? I'll take
'em right off yer hands!
What's that? Ya don't know what
'Spare Plates' are...?
Well, y'know, when you repair
plates back at the DigiLab,
If ya already got that plate, ya 
don't need it anymore, right?
Since ya can't put it into the
Evolution Tree, after all.
So it gets put into your Digivice's
'Consumables' section.
But isn't it a waste to leave them
plates there collectin' dust?!
So what I do is I take those
unneeded plates off ya hands!
Not for free, of course, I'll be
sure to offer compensation!
Sounds like a good deal, eh?
That way we'll both be happy♪
So then let's get started...
Have ya got 5 Spare Plates?
translation:
Yo! Thanks for comin'!
The name's Octomon!
Got any 'Spare Plates'? I'll take
'em right off yer hands!
What's that? Ya don't know what
'Spare Plates' are...?
Well, y'know, when you repair
plates back at the DigiLab,
If ya already got that plate, ya 
don't need it anymore, right?
Since ya can't put it into the
Evolution Tree, after all.
So it gets put into your Digivice's
'Consumables' section.
But isn't it a waste to leave them
plates there collectin' dust?!
So what I do is I take those
unneeded plates off ya hands!
Not for free, of course, I'll be
sure to offer compensation!
Sounds like a good deal, eh?
That way we'll both be happy♪
So then let's get started...
Have ya got 5 Spare Plates?
